added.title: The Dream Team
added.description: Craig and his cousin, Bryson, join forces for an action packed weekend at their grandparents house.

added.title: Fire & Ice
added.description: Kelsey and Stacks write a story for book club, which turns out to be more personal than Kelsey realized.

added.title: The Lonely Haunts Club 3: La Llorona
added.description: When Val sets out to get a little privacy in the woods, Vic is bent on pranking his unsuspecting brother,  that is, until Val goes missing.

added.title: Ghosted
added.description: Vic makes a ghost friend but when she interferes with his shot at being part of the cool kids' Tlatchtli team, he must choose between the two.

added.title: Love at First Bite
added.description: Val crushes on a girl named Matty, who Vic is suspicious of but Val ignores his warnings. When Val goes to dinner at her house she turns into a Matlazihua and he discovers he's what's for dinner!

added.title: #SweetJustice Part 1
added.description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

added.title: #SweetJustice Part 2
added.description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

added.title: #SweetJustice Part 3
added.description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

added.title: #SweetJustice Part 4
added.description: When six ordinary girls meet and discover that they each have extraordinary powers, they decide to join forces to take on one of Metropolis's most sinister villains.

added.title: #AdventuresInBunnysitting
added.description: Zee asks Kara to look after her two magical bunnies, which quickly start to multiply, wreaking havoc all across Metropolis.

added.title: Wednesday - Part 1
added.description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

added.title: Wednesday - Part 2
added.description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

added.title: Snarf's Day Off
added.description: Hey everyone, it's Snarf's monthly day off! That's right, this episode follows Snarf as he leaves Cats' Lair to get a needed vacation, by transforming into a normal cat and hanging out with a nice old lady on a farm! But his relaxing day is threatened when Snarf and the nice old lady cross paths with Mumm-Ra!

added.title: Mandora's Law
added.description: Tygra creates a bunch of new laws for Third Earth so Mandora can finally arrest the Mutants. Unfortunately the Thundercats are really bad at following their own rules and the Mutants are really good at working around them.

added.title: Thunder Road
added.description: When a crate containing fifty Swords of Omen lands on Third Earth, the ThunderCats rush out in the ThunderTank to find them. Unfortunately The Mutants and Mumm-Ra want those swords too so it's going to be a race to get to them! A wacky race, you might say. We won't say that, but you might.

added.title: Corporate Buyout
added.description: The Cheetara Corp employee retreat gets canceled when Baron Karnon, a mysterious corporate raider, buys them out! Now Cheetara and Jan-Jan must brave the wilds of Third Earth's most dangerous jungles to find the Baron's office and demand a meeting with the man who stole their company!

added.title: Hachiman
added.description: While on a super important mission to get batteries for the TV remote Lion-O meets Hachiman, a cool Samurai warrior. Now Lion-O will do anything to prove he's just as cool as Hachiman, even if it means risking his own life!

added.title: Everything's Fine
added.description: Steven insists that everything is fine.

added.title: I Am My Monster
added.description: Everything is not fine.

added.title: King Axel
added.description: After a screening of the King Arthur tale, Axel holds out his sword and declares himself king, but when Dynamo uses his magnetism to steal the weapon and bestow it upon Masko, it casts doubt among the team over who is the true leader.

added.title: The Trojan Bear
added.description: When Axel opens a subscription gift-box he didn't even order, the team finds their ranks divided by a robotic bear - or Princess SugarSalt in disguise!

added.title: Thirst for Power
added.description: Axel and his toys deploy the Joyride in a "ship" to "ship" battle against Dr. Nautilus, who has punctured a water main to flood the sewers and established himself as "Admiral Nautilus."

added.title: Party On
added.description: As Zoe preps Cleo LeBall's birthday party, Axel and the team run damage control against a jealous crasher - Princess SugarSalt, who has turned the decorations and gifts into instruments of chaos!

added.title: Bringing Up Baby
added.description: Zoe leaves Axel in charge of the school project - watching over an infant simulator doll - but when MadCap brings the doll to life, Axel and the team must stop the baby without damaging it or risk getting a failing grade!

added.title: Bakugan Battle Circus/Ebony Manor
added.description: Shun and Dan head to the Bakugan circus for a little fun, but the fun is interrupted when the star Bakugan are too exhausted to perform. Shun and Dan know the show must go on, and step in to lend a hand. Things go as planned until the evil Ringleader attempts to bring down the big top performance./ Lightning reunites with an old frenemy - Ebony. This time the kitty queen of the streets has a new home and is living a life of luxury with her new master.

added.title: Everett's Trap/Kazami vs. Mc Q
added.description: Shun and Masato head to Tokyo's Battle Island to discuss plans for hosting public Bakugan battles. Upon landing, they quickly learn it's a set up! The two are now stranded and faced with heaps of brawlers, who are all looking to bring them down!/ Shun and Masato manage to fend off a horde of brawlers on Battle Island, but they quickly learn that was only a diversion- one of Kazami's research centers is under siege. The two must find a way off the island and head off to defend the research center.

added.title: The Awesome Burger Brawl/Master and Apprentice
added.description: The Burger Joint is hosting a hamburger eating contest to promote their new Bakugan themed burger! The contest gets underway without a hitch, that is until Sophie and the Bakugan Preservation Society crash the event with a bakugan brawl!/ A wealthy man, Mr. Gold, has duped Storm and Ajit, and trapped them in his personal prison. But no prison can hold the cunning phantom thief Storm and his former apprentice, Ajit for long.

added.title: Bakugan Uproar/The Fusion Bakugan Sabrus
added.description: While the Awesome Brawlers' Bakugan squabble about what to watch on TV at Studio D, Haavik unleashes his newly created five-faction fusion Bakugan: Sabrus on the city of Los Volmos./ The Awesome Brawlers are in pursuit of Haavik and his new Bakugan, Sabrus but all they can find is the trail of destruction that Sabrus has left behind. They need to figure out where Haavik and his Bakugan will strike next and put an end to his rampage.

added.title: Ancient Golden Bakugan Garillion/The Name of Infinity
added.description: The ancient golden Bakugan, Garillion Infinity has come to Los Volmos to try to put an end to Haavik's show of destruction and chaos but upon arriving he turns his sights on Drago, Dan and the Awesome Brawlers./ Haavik and his five-faction fusion Bakugan Sabrus take their rampage to AAAnimus' headquarters. The Awesome Brawlers quickly track down the rampaging duo and face off!

added.title: No Shortcuts
added.description: After struggling to keep up, Adorabat gets a cybernetic "Mega-Mech." But can fancy new powers make up for experience?

added.title: Ultraclops
added.description: Badgerclops gets huge to destroy a towering monster, but when he refuses to shrink down, the kingdom faces a new terror.

added.title: Mao Mao's Bike Adventure
added.description: When Mao Mao underestimates enemy and friend alike, it almost costs him the entire kingdom.

added.title: Breakup
added.description:
Feeling left out, Adorabat wishes Mao Mao and Badgerclops would spend less time with each other and more time with her. When she gets
what she wishes for and accidentally breaks up their friendship, only the secret of their past can bring them back together.

added.title: Not Impressed
added.description: When a Sweetypie isn't impressed with the sheriff dept's antics, our three heroes try everything to win him over.

added.title: Amor a primera mordida
added.description: A Val le gusta una chica llamada Matty, y Vic sospecha de ella, pero Val ignora sus advertencias. Cuando Val va a su casa a cenar, ella se convierte en una Matlazihua, iy Val descubre que él es la cena!

added.title: El Libro Final
added.description: El último libro de fantasía de la serie favorita de Kelsey desaparece de la biblioteca. Por eso, Craig decide ayudarla a resolver el misterio de quién se lo llevó.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Demasiados Tesoros
added.description: Con la esperanza de reparar su fuerte, Craig consigue la ayuda de Los Veloces Diez para llevarlos hasta la legendaria pila de basura.
added.originalseriesname: Craig of the Creek en Espanol

added.title: Potencial Desperdiciado
added.description: A raíz de la victoria de la temporada anterior, los ninjas se han ablandado y el Maestro Wu debe recordarles quiénes son realmente.

added.title: Buscando Misiones
added.description: Al darse cuenta de que se han ablandado, el ninja busca una misión para reactivar su entrenamiento de Spinjitzu. Desafortunadamente, la ciudad de NINJAGO está disfrutando de un período de rara tranquilidad.

added.title: Un Comienzo Dificil
added.description: iLos ninja han encontrado su búsqueda! Ahora solo tienen que llegar allí, lo que implica un viaje por carretera a través del desierto de Doom, una región supuestamente habitada por un escarabajo gigante.

added.title: Sin Atajos
added.description: Tras esforzarse por mantener el ritmo en las batallas, Adorabat consigue una armadura cibernética. ¿Pero podrán unos nuevos y sofisticados poderes compensar la falta de experiencia?

added.title: Ultracolosal
added.description: Colosal se vuelve enorme para destruir a un monstruo altísimo, pero cuando se rehúsa a volver a su tamaño normal, el reino se enfrenta a un nuevo terror… el apetito insaciable de Colosal.

added.title: El Vientre del Monstruo
added.description: Para reparar el Land-Bounty, el ninja debe recuperar un componente crítico del motor que ha sido tragado por un escarabajo gigante.

added.title: La Aventura de la Moto de Mao Mao
added.description: Cuando Mao Mao subestima por igual a sus enemigos y a sus amigos, por poco le cuesta el reino entero.

added.title: Trampas y Como Sobrevivir a Ellas
added.description: El ninja se une a un clutch Powers renuente para entrar en una misteriosa pirámide donde desatan sin darse cuenta un antiguo mal.

added.title: Separacion
added.description: Adorabat siente que es dejada de lado y desea que Mao Mao y Colosal pasen menos tiempo juntos y más tiempo con ella. Pero cuando el deseo de Adorabat se hace realidad y destruye la amistad de Mao Mao y Colosal, solo el secreto de su pasado podrá volver a unirlos.

added.title: No Me Impresiona
added.description: Cuando un Corazoncito no se siente impresionado con las hazañas del departamento del sheriff, nuestros tres héroes intentan de todo para conquistarlo.

added.title: Todo Esta Bien
added.description: Steven insiste en que todo está bien.

added.title: Soy Mi Monstruo
added.description: No todo está bien.

added.title: Rey Axel
added.description: Después de una proyección de la historia del Rey Arturo, Axel extiende su espada y se declara rey, pero cuando Dynamo usa su magnetismo para robar el arma y dársela a Masko, arroja dudas entre el equipo sobre quién es el verdadero líder.

added.title: El Oso Troyano
added.description: Cuando Axel abre una caja de regalo de suscripción que ni siquiera ordenó, el equipo encuentra sus filas divididas por un oso robótico, io la Princesa SugarSalt disfrazada!

added.title: Sed de Poder
added.description: Axel y sus juguetes despliegan el Joyride en una batalla de "barco" a "barco" contra el Dr. Nautilus, quien ha perforado una tubería de agua para inundar las alcantarillas y se ha establecido como "Almirante Nautilus".

added.title: Que Comience la Fiesta
added.description: Mientras Zoe prepara la fiesta de cumpleaños de Cleo LeBall, Axel y el equipo controlan los daños contra una estrelladora celosa: ila princesa SugarSalt, que ha convertido las decoraciones y los regalos en instrumentos de caos!

added.title: Criando Bebe
added.description: Zoe deja a Axel a cargo del proyecto escolar, vigilando una muñeca simulador de bebés, pero cuando MadCap da vida a la muñeca, iAxel y el equipo deben detener al bebé sin dañarlo o correr el riesgo de obtener una calificación reprobatoria!
